Plot the target

target <- train %>%
  group_by(target) %>%
  summarise(counts = n())
ggplot(target, aes(x = target, y = counts)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", fill='lightblue')+
  geom_text(aes(label = counts), vjust = -0.4)

## plot the keyword

keyword <- train %>%
  group_by(keyword) %>%
  summarise(counts = n(), rate = mean(target)) %>%
  arrange(counts, desc(counts))

#### filter out > 40
keyword40 <- filter(keyword, counts>40)
ggplot(keyword40, aes(x=keyword,  y=counts)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill='lightblue') + 
  geom_text(aes(label=counts), vjust = -0.4)

## filter high rate rate out

keywordrate <- filter(keyword, rate>0.6 & counts>35)
ggplot(keywordrate, aes(x=keyword,  y=counts)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill='lightblue') + 
  geom_text(aes(label=round(rate, digit = 2)), vjust = -0.4)+
  theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle = 90,vjust = 0))

## location

location <- train %>%
  group_by(location) %>%
  summarise(counts = n(), rate = mean(target)) %>%
  arrange(counts, desc(counts))
#### filter out > 30
location30 <- filter(location, counts >30)
ggplot(location30, aes(x=location,  y=counts)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill='lightblue') + 
  geom_text(aes(label=counts), vjust = -0.4)

## filter high rate

locationrate <- filter(location, rate>0.5 & counts>10)
ggplot(locationrate, aes(x=location,  y=counts)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill='lightblue') + 
  geom_text(aes(label=round(rate, digit = 2)), vjust = -0.4)+
  theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle = 90,vjust = 0))

Text Processing

transform to corpus

cleaning

corpus_clean <- tm_map(corpus, removePunctuation)
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(corpus, removePunctuation): transformation drops
## documents
corpus_clean <- tm_map(corpus_clean, removeWords, stopwords("english"))
## Warning in tm_map.SimpleCorpus(corpus_clean, removeWords, stopwords("english")):
## transformation drops documents
corpus_clean <- tm_map(corpus_clean, removeNumbers)
